cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the use of data augmentation as a regularization technique in deep neural networks, which is a common topic in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also analyzes the effect of data augmentation on different architectures, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) in some of the experiments.
